# Scots

## Places to start

### Adding new words

Find frequent words, and add them

    cat some_tokens | apertium -d . sco-tagger | grep '*' | sort | uniq -c | sort -n

## References

 * scots-online.org - contains a grammar!
 * www.scotslanguage.com - text, podcasts, all sorts of things


